name: Frog Demo
overview: This prototype was found in a box of EPROMs given to the Digital Press by Dr. John Bronstein, one of the co-founders of Commavid. This EPROM was simply labeled "Frog", and is really just a one-screen demo featuring a frog and some stationary moths. When the fire button is pressed, the frog will shoot out its tongue (looks suspiciously like the laser beam).
